{"tid":1453413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓外務省全力支持中國黨和政府解決香港事態的立場與措施  並反對外部勢力干預，破壞香港","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:31:44.000Z","uid":133680,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bd4bc112fd6e9768d9c2c722ca0777790359a33f","tid":1453413,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:09:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/139543009419663/posts/3254223684618231/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F139543009419663%2Fposts%2F3254223684618231%2F&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=293db037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/139543009419663/posts/3254223684618231/</a><br />\n<br />\n【金仔力撐習大大】據朝中社報道，北韓外務省發言人表示，全力支持中國黨和政府解決香港事態的立場與措施。<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2H3c6EO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H3c6EO&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=d70b8fc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2H3c6EO</a><br />\n<br />\n發言人指出，最近，外部勢力赤裸裸企圖干涉純屬中國內政的香港事務、破壞香港社會的安全和秩序，損害市民的生命和財產，北韓對此表示關切及反對。<br />\n<br />\n發言人強調，北韓的原則立場是，香港是中國的香港，不容許任何國家、組織和個人，破壞中國主權、安全和「一國兩制」的行徑，北韓全力支持中國黨和政府為捍衞國家主權、安全、領土完整和香港繁榮穩定採取的立場和措施。<br />\n<br />\n#信報 #反修例 #北韓"},{"pid":"80679b818088a7514d8dd0c7404fd60fe823ab0a","tid":1453413,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:10:17.000Z","msg":"睇唔透係金仔真心定侵侵指示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888c84e4bfc195e509b73a72292d13dc254580d5","tid":1453413,"uid":201178,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"中國搵外國勢力都搵個名聲好d嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fda57ec566668d6d15c644c2222335d9f06d4f1","tid":1453413,"uid":127328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:11:32.000Z","msg":"抽水，全力標籤港共係恐怖政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" clas